Build process:

  Create an NSIS installer script for Windows.


Ports:

  Windows
    Script to install compiler, libraries, etc:
      http://www.sandroid.org/imcross/
    Cross-develompent tools:
      MinGW cross-compiler:
        http://www.mingw.org/
        http://mingw-cross.sourceforge.net/
        http://www.mingw.org/MinGWiki/index.php/build%20a%20Win32%20x-compiler%20for%20Linux
        http://members.lycos.co.uk/alexv6/Cross_mingw_building_HOWTO.html
      Cross-compiling GTK+ apps:
        http://live.gnome.org/GTK%2B/Win32/Apps

      mingw32 on Fedora:
        http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/MinGW

        tools in /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/bin
        DLLs in /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/bin
                /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/lib/pango/1.6.0/modules
                /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/lib/gtk-2.0/2.10.0/loaders
                /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/lib/gtk-2.0/2.10.0/engines
                /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/lib/gtk-2.0/2.10.0/immodules
                /usr/i686-pc-mingw32/sys-root/mingw/lib/gtk-2.0/modules

    Libraries and Toolkits:
      GTK+ for Windows:  http://www.gtk.org/download-windows.html
                         ftp://ftp.gtk.org/pub/gtk/v2.8/win32/
			 http://www.gimp.org/~tml/gimp/win32/
			 http://live.gnome.org/GTK%2B/Win32

      GTK+ for Windows runtime installer:
			 http://gimp-win.sourceforge.net/stable.html
		(not compatible with Gimp installer when I last tried it):
                          http://gtk-win.sourceforge.net/home/index.php/en/Home

      libxml2 for Windows:   http://www.zlatkovic.com/libxml.en.html
      SDL for Windows:       http://www.libsdl.org/

    Installers:
      NSIS:        http://nsis.sourceforge.net/
      MAKEMSI:     http://www.labyrinth.net.au/~dbareis/makemsi.htm
      WiX:         http://sourceforge.net/projects/wix/

    Note that the Windows version of GAIM uses GTK+ and NSIS, so it may
    be a useful reference:
      http://gaim.sourceforge.net/win32/

    Python/PyGTK/GTK installer:
      http://aruiz.typepad.com/siliconisland/2006/12/allinone_win32_.html

  MacOS X
    http://www.macgimp.org/index.php?topic=gtk
    http://developer.imendio.com/projects/gtk-macosx/
    http://www.macports.org/
